CASE WHEN (@gp3 = @p__linq__1) THEN (`Extent4`.`ENUS`)  WHEN (@gp4 = @p__linq__2) THEN (`Extent4`.`DEDE`)  WHEN (@gp5 = @p__linq__3) THEN (`Extent4`.`ZHCN`)  WHEN (@gp6 = @p__linq__4) THEN (`Extent4`.`JAJP`)  WHEN (@gp7 = @p__linq__5) THEN (`Extent4`.`VIVN`)  ELSE (`Extent4`.`KOKR`) END AS `C1`, 
SUBSTR(`Filter1`.`URL`, 1 + 1, 4) AS `C2`, 
SUBSTR(`Filter1`.`URL`, 6 + 1, 8) AS `C3`
FROM (SELECT
`Extent1`.`MENUID`, 
`Extent1`.`MENUCODE`, 
`Extent1`.`MENUNAME`, 
`Extent1`.`PARENTMENUID`, 
`Extent1`.`CONTENTID`, 
`Extent1`.`DISPLAYSEQ`, 
`Extent1`.`MENULEVEL`, 
`Extent1`.`URL`, 
`Extent1`.`MENUICON`, 
`Extent1`.`DISPLAYYN`, 
`Extent1`.`USEYN`, 
`Extent1`.`MEMO`, 
`Extent1`.`CREATEDATE`, 
`Extent1`.`CREATEUSER`, 
`Extent1`.`RECENTDATE`, 
`Extent1`.`RECENTUSER`, 
`Extent2`.`EMPFAVORITEMENUID`, 
`Extent2`.`EMPCODE`, 
`Extent2`.`MENUCODE` AS `MENUCODE1`, 
`Extent2`.`USEYN` AS `USEYN1`, 
`Extent2`.`CREATEUSER` AS `CREATEUSER1`,

`Extent3`.`AUTHORITYID`,

`Extent3`.`HMIYN`, 
`Extent3`.`CREATEUSER` AS `CREATEUSER2`, 
`Extent3`.`CREATEDATE` AS `CREATEDATE2`, 
`Extent3`.`RECENTUSER` AS `RECENTUSER2`, 
`Extent3`.`RECENTDATE` AS `RECENTDATE2`
FROM `T2_MENU_MASTER` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN `T2_EMP_FAVORITE_MENU_MASTER` AS `Extent2` ON `Extent1`.`MENUCODE` = `Extent2`.`MENUCODE` INNER JOIN `T2_EMP_AUTHORITY` AS `Extent3` ON `Extent1`.`MENUCODE` = `Extent3`.`MENUCODE`
 WHERE ((@gp1 = `Extent1`.`USEYN`) AND (@gp2 = `Extent2`.`USEYN`)) AND (1 = `Extent3`.`VIEWYN`)) AS `Filter1` LEFT OUTER JOIN `T2_LANG_MASTER` AS `Extent4` ON `Filter1`.`MENUID` = `Extent4`.`LANGID`

`Project1`.`FIFO_LOTNUMBER`
FROM (SELECT
`Extent1`.`SERIALNUMBER`, 
`Extent1`.`LOTNUMBER`, 
`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER`, 
`Extent1`.`INVENTQUANTITY`, 
`Extent2`.`MATERIALNAME`, 
`Extent2`.`UNITCODE`, 
`Extent3`.`FIFO_LOTNUMBER`, 
CASE WHEN (@gp1 = `Extent2`.`UNITCODE`) THEN ((`Extent1`.`INVENTQUANTITY`) / 1000)  ELSE (`Extent1`.`INVENTQUANTITY`) END AS `C1`, 
CASE WHEN (@gp2 = `Extent2`.`UNITCODE`) THEN ((`Extent1`.`INVENTQUANTITY`) / 1000)  ELSE (`Extent1`.`INVENTQUANTITY`) END AS `C2`
FROM `T4_MATERIAL_STOCK` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN `T2_MATERIAL_MASTER` AS `Extent2` ON `Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`MATERIALCODE` INNER JOIN `T4_LOTMASTER` AS `Extent3` ON `Extent1`.`SERIALNUMBER` = `Extent3`.`SERIALNUMBER`) AS `Project1`
 ORDER BY 
`Project1`.`FIFO_LOTNUMBER` ASC, 
`Project1`.`SERIALNUMBER` ASC

FROM `T4_WORKRESULT` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN `T2_PARTNUMBER_MASTER` AS `Extent2` ON `Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`PARTNUMBER` LEFT OUTER JOIN `T2_PROCESS_MASTER` AS `Extent3` ON (`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE` = `Extent3`.`PROCESSCODE`) AND (@gp1 = `Extent3`.`USEYN`)
 WHERE ((@gp2 = `Extent2`.`USEYN`) AND (`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` >= @gp3)) AND (`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` < @gp4)) AS `Project1`
 ORDER BY 
`Project1`.`WORKDATE` DESC, 
`Project1`.`PARTNUMBER` ASC, 
`Project1`.`PROCESSCODE` ASC,

FROM `T4_WORKRESULT` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN `T3_WORKORDER` AS `Extent2` ON (((`Extent1`.`ORDERNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`ORDERNUMBER`) AND (`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE` = `Extent2`.`PROCESSCODE`)) AND ((`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` = `Extent2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`) OR ((`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL) AND (`Extent2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL)))) AND (`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`PARTNUMBER`) INNER JOIN `T2_PARTNUMBER_MASTER` AS `Extent3` ON `Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent3`.`PARTNUMBER` LEFT OUTER JOIN `T2_PROCESS_MASTER` AS `Extent4` ON (`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE` = `Extent4`.`PROCESSCODE`) AND (@gp1 = `Extent4`.`USEYN`)
 WHERE ((`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` >= @gp2) AND (`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` < @gp3)) AND (@gp4 = `Extent3`.`USEYN`)) AS `GroupBy1`

FROM (SELECT

`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`,

CASE WHEN (@gp5 = `Extent4`.`PROCESSGROUP`) THEN (`Extent1`.`WORKSTARTTIME`)  ELSE (`Extent1`.`WORKENDTIME`) END AS `C1`, 
CASE WHEN (0 = `Extent1`.`PRODUCTQUANTITY`) THEN (0)  ELSE ((`Extent1`.`PRODUCTQUANTITY` / `Extent2`.`ORDERQUANTITY`) * 100) END AS `C2`, 
CASE WHEN (0 = `Extent1`.`GOODQUANTITY`) THEN (0)  ELSE ((`Extent1`.`GOODQUANTITY` / `Extent1`.`PRODUCTQUANTITY`) * 100) END AS `C3`, 
CASE WHEN (0 = `Extent1`.`DEFECTQUANTITY`) THEN (0)  ELSE ((`Extent1`.`DEFECTQUANTITY` / `Extent1`.`PRODUCTQUANTITY`) * 100) END AS `C4`
FROM `T4_WORKRESULT` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN `T3_WORKORDER` AS `Extent2` ON (((`Extent1`.`ORDERNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`ORDERNUMBER`) AND (`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE` = `Extent2`.`PROCESSCODE`)) AND ((`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` = `Extent2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`) OR ((`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL) AND (`Extent2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL)))) AND (`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`PARTNUMBER`) INNER JOIN `T2_PARTNUMBER_MASTER` AS `Extent3` ON `Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent3`.`PARTNUMBER` LEFT OUTER JOIN `T2_PROCESS_MASTER` AS `Extent4` ON (`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE` = `Extent4`.`PROCESSCODE`) AND (@gp1 = `Extent4`.`USEYN`)
 WHERE ((`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` >= @gp2) AND (`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` < @gp3)) AND (@gp4 = `Extent3`.`USEYN`)) AS `Project1`

`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` AS `K4`, 
`Extent1`.`SHIFTCODE` AS `K5`, 
`Extent1`.`PLANTCODE` AS `K6`, 
`Extent4`.`PRODUCTNAME` AS `K7`, 
SUM(`Extent1`.`PRODUCTQUANTITY`) AS `A1`, 
SUM(`Join1`.`A1`) AS `A2`, 
SUM(`Join1`.`A1`) AS `A3`, 
SUM(`Extent1`.`PRODUCTQUANTITY`) AS `A4`
FROM `T4_WORKRESULT` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN (SELECT
`GroupBy1`.`K1`, 
`GroupBy1`.`K2`, 
`GroupBy1`.`K3`, 
`GroupBy1`.`K4`, 
`GroupBy1`.`A1`, 
`Distinct1`.`SERIALNUMBER`, 
`Distinct1`.`PARTNUMBER`, 
`Distinct1`.`PROCESSCODE`, 
`Distinct1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`, 
`Distinct1`.`ORDERNUMBER`
FROM (SELECT
`Extent2`.`SERIALNUMBER` AS `K1`, 
`Extent2`.`PARTNUMBER` AS `K2`, 
`Extent2`.`PROCESSCODE` AS `K3`, 
`Extent2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` AS `K4`, 
SUM(`Extent2`.`DEFECTQUANTITY`) AS `A1`
FROM `T5_DEFECT_HISTORY` AS `Extent2`
 GROUP BY 
`Extent2`.`SERIALNUMBER`, 
`Extent2`.`PARTNUMBER`, 
`Extent2`.`PROCESSCODE`, 
`Extent2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`) AS `GroupBy1` INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT 
`Extent3`.`SERIALNUMBER`, 
`Extent3`.`PARTNUMBER`, 
`Extent3`.`PROCESSCODE`, 
`Extent3`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`, 
`Extent3`.`ORDERNUMBER`
FROM `T5_WIP_HISTORY` AS `Extent3`) AS `Distinct1` ON (((`GroupBy1`.`K3` = `Distinct1`.`PROCESSCODE`) OR ((`GroupBy1`.`K3` IS  NULL) AND (`Distinct1`.`PROCESSCODE` IS  NULL))) AND ((`GroupBy1`.`K4` = `Distinct1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`) OR ((`GroupBy1`.`K4` IS  NULL) AND (`Distinct1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL)))) AND (`GroupBy1`.`K2` = `Distinct1`.`PARTNUMBER`)) AS `Join1` ON ((((`Extent1`.`ORDERNUMBER` = `Join1`.`ORDERNUMBER`) OR ((`Extent1`.`ORDERNUMBER` IS  NULL) AND (`Join1`.`ORDERNUMBER` IS  NULL))) AND (`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE` = `Join1`.`PROCESSCODE`)) AND ((`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` = `Join1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`) OR ((`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL) AND (`Join1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` IS  NULL)))) AND (`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Join1`.`PARTNUMBER`) INNER JOIN `T2_PARTNUMBER_MASTER` AS `Extent4` ON `Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent4`.`PARTNUMBER`
 WHERE ((`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` >= @gp1) AND (`Extent1`.`WORKDATE` < @gp2)) AND (@gp3 = `Extent4`.`USEYN`)
 GROUP BY 
`Extent1`.`WORKDATE`, 
`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER`, 
`Extent1`.`PROCESSCODE`, 
`Extent1`.`EQUIPMENTCODE`, 
`Extent1`.`SHIFTCODE`, 
`Extent1`.`PLANTCODE`, 
`Extent4`.`PRODUCTNAME`) AS `GroupBy2`) AS `Project2`
 ORDER BY 
`Project2`.`WORKDATE` DESC, 
`Project2`.`PARTNUMBER` ASC, 
`Project2`.`PROCESSCODE` ASC, 
`Project2`.`EQUIPMENTCODE` ASC, 
`Project2`.`C1` ASC LIMIT 25

`Project1`.`C2`, 
`Project1`.`C3`, 
`Project1`.`C4`
FROM (SELECT

`Filter1`.`PARENTMENUID`, 
`Filter1`.`CONTENTID`, 
`Filter1`.`DISPLAYSEQ`, 
`Filter1`.`MENULEVEL`, 
`Filter1`.`MENUICON`, 
CASE WHEN (@gp3 = @p__linq__1) THEN (`Extent4`.`ENUS`)  WHEN (@gp4 = @p__linq__2) THEN (`Extent4`.`DEDE`)  WHEN (@gp5 = @p__linq__3) THEN (`Extent4`.`ZHCN`)  WHEN (@gp6 = @p__linq__4) THEN (`Extent4`.`JAJP`)  WHEN (@gp7 = @p__linq__5) THEN (`Extent4`.`VIVN`)  ELSE (`Extent4`.`KOKR`) END AS `C1`, 
SUBSTR(`Filter1`.`URL`, 1 + 1, 4) AS `C2`, 
SUBSTR(`Filter1`.`URL`, 6 + 1, 8) AS `C3`, 
CASE WHEN (`Filter1`.`EMPCODE1` IS NOT NULL) THEN (@gp9)  ELSE (@gp8) END AS `C4`
FROM (SELECT
`Extent1`.`MENUID`,

FROM ((SELECT
@gp1 AS `C1`, 
`Extent2`.`WIPSEQUENCE`, 
`Extent2`.`ORDERNUMBER`,

`Extent2`.`LOTNUMBER`,

FROM `T5_WIP_HISTORY` AS `Extent2`) UNION ALL (SELECT
@gp2 AS `C1`,

`Extent3`.`ORDERNUMBER`,

`Extent3`.`CREATEUSER`
FROM `T5_MATERIAL_WIP_HISTORY` AS `Extent3`)) AS `UnionAll1`) AS `Distinct1` ON (`Extent1`.`ORDERNUMBER` = `Distinct1`.`C3`) AND (`Extent1`.`ORDERSEQUENCE` = `Distinct1`.`C4`) LEFT OUTER JOIN `T2_PARTNUMBER_MASTER` AS `Extent4` ON `Distinct1`.`C7` = `Extent4`.`PARTNUMBER` LEFT OUTER JOIN `T2_MATERIAL_MASTER` AS `Extent5` ON `Distinct1`.`C7` = `Extent5`.`MATERIALCODE`
 WHERE (((`Distinct1`.`C17`) >= @gp3) AND ((`Distinct1`.`C17`) < @gp4)) AND ((@gp5 = `Distinct1`.`C1`) OR (@gp6 = `Distinct1`.`C1`))) AS `Project4`
 ORDER BY 
`Project4`.`C7` ASC, 
`Project4`.`C5` DESC, 
`Project4`.`C9` ASC, 
`Project4`.`C8` DESC, 
`Project4`.`C6` DESC

FROM (SELECT
`GroupBy1`.`A1` AS `C1`, 
`GroupBy1`.`A2` AS `C2`, 
`GroupBy1`.`K1` AS `PARTNUMBER`, 
1 AS `C3`
FROM (SELECT
`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` AS `K1`, 
COUNT(1) AS `A1`, 
SUM(`Extent1`.`QUANTITY`) AS `A2`
FROM `T4_PRODUCT_STOCK` AS `Extent1` INNER JOIN `T2_PARTNUMBER_MASTER` AS `Extent2` ON `Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER` = `Extent2`.`PARTNUMBER`
 WHERE @gp1 = `Extent2`.`USEYN`
 GROUP BY 
`Extent1`.`PARTNUMBER`) AS `GroupBy1`) AS `Project1`
 ORDER BY 
`Project1`.`PARTNUMBER` ASC

`Extent1`.`CREATEDATE` AS `C3`

 WHERE (`Extent1`.`TRANSCODE` IN ( @gp1,@gp2,@gp3 )) AND (((`Extent1`.`WORKDATE`) >= @gp4) AND ((`Extent1`.`WORKDATE`) < @gp5))) AS `Project1`
 ORDER BY 
`Project1`.`C1` DESC, 
`Project1`.`SERIALNUMBER` DESC, 
`Project1`.`MATERIALHISSEQ` DESC LIMIT 25
